data.description: Indulge in luxury living at its finest with this fully renovated condo in a gated community! With upgraded flooring, taller baseboards, granite countertops, and trendy can lights throughout, this home is a true gem.  Perfectly located just minutes away from popular shopping centers and a quick hop onto the freeway. Step into a modern living space designed for both relaxation and entertaining. The community provides an array of amenities including a gym, pool/hot tub, sauna, clubhouse, mailroom, snow removal, and partial utilities.
